collapse.paragraphs:
 We have:
\begin{multline*}
x^4 + x^3 +  1 = (x^2 + x + 1)(x^2 + x + 1)\\
= x^4 + 2x^3 + 3x^2 + 2x + 1 = x^4 + x^2 + 1,
\end{multline*}
a contradiction.

